name: Maruti Plast
overview:
Established in the year 1999, we, “Maruti Plast”, are one of the distinguished organizations that are engaged in manufacturing and supplying a comprehensive assortment of finest quality Furniture Nylon Caster Wheel, Trolley Nylon Caster Wheel, Table Nylon Caster Wheel, PU Nylon Caster Wheel and Stainless Steel Nylon Caster Wheel.

Our Team: A team of highly skilled & qualified professionals is a main reason behind the immense success of our organization.

Our Quality Assurance: Being a quality conscious organization, we are manufacturing and supplying a broad assortment of premium quality Furniture Nylon Caster Wheel, Trolley Nylon Caster Wheel, Table Nylon Caster Wheel, PU Nylon Caster Wheel and Stainless Steel Nylon Caster Wheel.

Infrastructure: To form a strong base for us to carry out all business operations with ease, we have developed a state-of-the-art infrastructure facility.

Client Satisfaction: Ours’ is a client-oriented organization, which put its sincere dedication & efforts to acquire customers utmost satisfaction.

Why Us: Our entire range of Furniture Nylon Caster Wheel, Trolley Nylon Caster Wheel, Table Nylon Caster Wheel, PU Nylon Caster Wheel and Stainless Steel Nylon Caster Wheel is widely demanded in the market for its high quality and on-time delivery.
